From: Li Zhou <li.zhou@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 15 Jan 2019 10:11:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] mxc: replace get_user_pages() write/force parameters with
 gup_flags

Replace get_user_pages() write/force parameters with gup_flags
in mxc codes, because the parameters of get_user_pages
function have been changed as below:
-		    int write, int force, struct page **pages,
+		    unsigned int gup_flags, struct page **pages,

Here do the modification referring to the earlier commit:
<mm: replace get_user_pages() write/force parameters with gup_flags>

Signed-off-by: Li Zhou <li.zhou@windriver.com>
---
 .../gpu-viv/hal/os/linux/kernel/gc_hal_kernel_os.c |    3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/mxc/gpu-viv/hal/os/linux/kernel/gc_hal_kernel_os.c b/drivers/mxc/gpu-viv/hal/os/linux/kernel/gc_hal_kernel_os.c
index 58eec12..02d58f5 100644
--- a/drivers/mxc/gpu-viv/hal/os/linux/kernel/gc_hal_kernel_os.c
+++ b/drivers/mxc/gpu-viv/hal/os/linux/kernel/gc_hal_kernel_os.c
@@ -4946,8 +4946,7 @@ OnError:
                     current->mm,
                     memory & PAGE_MASK,
                     pageCount,
-                    1,
-                    0,
+                    FOLL_WRITE,
                     pages,
                     gcvNULL
                     );
